WEBVTT

00:04.923 --> 00:09.269
I'm the manager of this department and that is Jane, our secretary.

00:12.029 --> 00:15.053
I'm going to take a walk outside and buy a cup of coffee.

00:17.581 --> 00:22.423
I have a lot of work to do today, but I will be on vacation in the next few days.

00:25.282 --> 00:29.721
Tina wants to join the meeting, but she has to finish some important work.

00:32.283 --> 00:33.557
You've worked so hard!

00:33.827 --> 00:36.182
You can go out and have a break or take a nap.

00:39.074 --> 00:43.221
You can help us carry the boxes upstairs or stay here to look after the van.

